BTW the preOrder BST traversal function can be written much more cleanly:

  preOrder(node = this.root) {
    if (!node) {
      return []
    }

    return [node.data, ...this.preOrder(node.left), ...this.preOrder(node.right)];
  }

it consumes more memory, but is faster this way. Pick your poison I guess

